# ADDED — These 3 files were causing merge conflicts when teammates pulled
# They are Android Studio IDE configuration files that each developer's
# machine generates differently based on their local setup (emulators,
# devices, SDK paths). They should never be committed to the shared repo
# because they are personal to each developer's machine.
